snippet.title: Plungeroo | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Plungeroo is a colorful puzzle game about tinkering with mini pinball cabinets, no quick reflexes or quarters required! Maneuver your ball through Pop Bumpers, Flippers, and more until you become a pinball wizard!

Coming to computers and mobile in October of 2023!
